author: Home Repair Tutor
description: Front door project tips…I’m using four @zipwall_llc poles with 4 mil plastic to enclose the space. I make the plastic 8 inches wider than the area. That way the plastic can be sealed against the walls with tape or Foam Rails. This is a great option for painting or doing other work on the door. Many thanks to ZipWall for sponsoring this tutorial 🔥#outdoorproject #zipwallbarriers #homerenovation #homerepairtutor #sponsored
